Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.98,0:00:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞維是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.05,0:00:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是機械的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.31,0:00:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於他們來說孩子只是備用零件而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.04,0:00:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在自己完全消磨完前繼承機能的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.39,0:00:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那個機械是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.16,0:00:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是被稱為亞維人類帝國的巨大而且邪惡的機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.76,0:00:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個邪惡的機械  健全的人類社會一直遭到威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.66,0:00:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且  如果允許其存在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.97,0:00:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天人類社會會被其完全吞併
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.24,0:00:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須要將其破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.66,0:01:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選自費滋達比多議員在人類統合體中央評議會上的演講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.00,0:02:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs18\fnMonotype Corsiva}www.dmhy.net
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.00,0:02:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs18}動漫花園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.00,0:01:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18\fnMonotype Corsiva}www.cnseikai.com
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.00,0:01:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18\fnMonotype Corsiva}bbs.cnseikai.com
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.00,0:01:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18}特別鳴謝：幻炎28分艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.00,0:01:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18}壓制：alex
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.00,0:01:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18}校對：basaka ashitaka
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.00,0:01:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18}翻譯：ashitaka
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.00,0:01:40.00,Default,,0000,0130,0000,,{\a3}哥斯羅斯號的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.15,0:02:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷利亞  報告情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位  前方78度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.55,0:03:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離1539.17天浬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.19,0:03:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進方向  前方18度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是史法格諾夫侯國方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.15,0:03:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已確認120個時空泡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.81,0:03:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總質量約為9000萬噸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是艦隊的話  其規模為4個分艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道是從哪個門進入的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,範圍縮小到47個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法再進一步縮小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.07,0:03:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些當中有正在使用的門嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.40,0:03:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  都是以關閉狀態放置著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.18,0:03:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1光年以內存在有人行星的門呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.25,0:03:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.14,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5光年以內呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.68,0:03:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.06,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離凱修193門4.1光年的巴斯科頓星系行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.52,0:03:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴斯科頓Ⅳ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.03,0:03:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其所屬是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類統合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方  時空泡群有變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時空泡1個分裂為10個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉向向我們駛來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.00,0:04:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從質量上來看是突擊艦級的單艦時空泡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.99,0:04:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長  進入第二級臨戰狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.03,0:04:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預定於艦內時間20點30分轉入第一級臨戰狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.73,0:04:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以  艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我重申一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是亞布里艾爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臨陣脫逃是亞布里艾爾的恥辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.54,0:04:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種豪言壯語還是等你戴上雙翼頭環後再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.44,0:04:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞布里艾爾·尼＝杜布雷斯克·帕留紐子爵·拉斐爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫臨陣脫逃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡並沒有你的戰鬥崗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是個未完成品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.46,0:04:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對這裡來說是多餘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我給了你一個任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.14,0:04:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將非戰鬥人員的伯爵公子閣下帶離戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.62,0:04:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並向帝國報告可能是敵人的艦隊正在接近的這個重大任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.53,0:05:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不願意接受這個任務才是臨陣脫逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.81,0:05:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連臨陣脫逃的意思也不懂的無能行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不以此為恥的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那亞布里艾爾就不值得接受亞維人的忠誠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.53,0:05:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再要爭辯的話我就以抗命罪逮捕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.76,0:05:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後的話你就等到在以嚴正聞名的皇前會議時陳述吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.85,0:05:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的想法錯了  艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在拉克法卡爾再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可愛的殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.74,0:06:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來歷不明的時空泡群進入了可通訊範圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報上我們的艦名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詢問對方來歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.61,0:06:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是挑戰信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.67,0:06:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下沒錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挑戰信號長鳴不止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要回訊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  隨它去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.73,0:06:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要玩的話  得先追上我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉斐爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我說拉斐爾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是帕留紐子爵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽聽關於你領地的事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.97,0:07:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕留紐子爵領是什麼樣的地方呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為「薔薇之國」的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有許多薔薇盛開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說薔薇了  連地衣類也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.31,0:07:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論哪個行星都連微生物都不存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼要叫薔薇之國呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.13,0:07:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為負責探察的是個喜歡花的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.09,0:07:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就隨便找些個花名一個個往上套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像百合之國啦  山茶之國啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是如此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.61,0:07:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～  那麼是怎樣的地方呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒什麼好說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一顆黃色的恆星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有7顆行星圍繞其旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.44,0:07:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二行星稍微改造一下的話說不定能住人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  當履行完皇族的義務後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想稍微去弄一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使其開滿薔薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以不負其「薔薇之國」之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.09,0:07:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.03,0:08:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想安慰我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.83,0:08:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很難說你很在行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.52,0:08:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你這份心意我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.36,0:08:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  我不會安慰人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.21,0:08:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的故鄉怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可和你不同  有很多事情可以說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想帶你去一次我的故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你在那裡住上幾年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.19,0:08:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等履行完皇族的義務後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帶我去也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊   一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.55,0:08:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算真的到了那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也只是稍微長大了一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樣子還是十分年輕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.42,0:08:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我卻已經非老即死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了  艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.26,0:09:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通告  我是艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.64,0:09:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來歷不明的時空泡群明白地表示了其敵意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始  轉移為第一級臨戰狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體進入戰鬥崗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體就位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備進行機雷戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.74,0:09:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向第7至第10號機雷注入反物質燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.49,0:09:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正向第7至第10號機雷注入反物質燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反物質燃料注入完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.13,0:10:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射出機雷  在時空泡內待機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機雷射出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機雷  已在時空泡內待機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.37,0:10:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣在演習中失去的1號至6號機雷還真有點可惜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.24,0:10:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是也不能太奢求了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.34,0:10:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方時空泡進入機雷射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.09,0:10:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊隊形簡直和教科書上一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機雷  生成時空泡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機雷  開始生成時空泡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認時空泡已生成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機雷瞄準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.45,0:11:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7-3  8-1  9-6  10-7
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.71,0:11:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,個體輸入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.33,0:11:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7-3  8-1  9-6  10-7
